{"tid":1959874,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有iPhone 9的日子","createTime":"2020-04-05T17:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T15:56:00.000Z","uid":60344,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ae51bc54b2ff8980dfc225b5eb91c2052acd76fd","tid":1959874,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T17:40:43.000Z","msg":"4月6日<br />\n沒有iPhone 9的第一日<br />\n雨<br />\n<br />\n終於有消息了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://external.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQBPkiq9NeDrdacF&amp;w=1000&amp;h=522&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2FiPhone-01.png&amp;cfs=1&amp;ext=jpg&amp;_nc_hash=AQARS_Fnj9F0cUWo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQBPkiq9NeDrdacF%26w%3D1000%26h%3D522%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcdn.unwire.hk%252Fwp-content%252Fuploads%252F2020%252F01%252FiPhone-01.png%26cfs%3D1%26ext%3Djpg%26_nc_hash%3DAQARS_Fnj9F0cUWo&h=6e256ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/03/iphone9/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR2nv-geqv4sprz6RH3RznzSs39e-vhn2qwfjKNjsIS3aZiIYG6NxwKM9no\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F03%2Fiphone9%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2nv-geqv4sprz6RH3RznzSs39e-vhn2qwfjKNjsIS3aZiIYG6NxwKM9no&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfzzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=f5ab2103\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/03/iphone9/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR2nv-geqv4sprz6RH3RznzSs39e-vhn2qwfjKNjsIS3aZiIYG6NxwKM9no</a><br />\n<br />\nA13 chip, 4.7&rdquo; Mon, Touch ID&hellip;&hellip; 無論你叫iPhone 9定SE 2，我都一樣咁期待！<br />\n<br />\n呢刻嘅心情真係又悲喜交集&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n悲係因為終於要同SE講拜拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />4年來，跌爆過、整過、換過電，去過旅行影過相，經歷過成長，真係唔捨得！<br />\n<br />\n不過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />作為一個由iPhone 4 開始決志嘅教徒，data喺肉身之間穿梭，衰老至新生，由4到SE，SE到將至嘅9，堅持「一手掌控生活」概念，覺得總算無愧教主在天之靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://9to5mac.com/2020/04/02/exclusive-iphone-9-launch-imminent-2020-iphone-se-in-red-white-and-black/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2020%2F04%2F02%2Fexclusive-iphone-9-launch-imminent-2020-iphone-se-in-red-white-and-black%2F&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfzzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=d4744b80\" target=\"_blank\">https://9to5mac.com/2020/04/02/exclusive-iphone-9-launch-imminent-2020-iphone-se-in-red-white-and-black/</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;iPhone 9 launch <strong>imminent</strong>&rdquo;&hellip; 真係急死寶寶了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090eff8ed5e81e8a5fee954bd0f861108b477010","tid":1959874,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"「傳」"},{"pid":"4a6a02b232fdc0c703ce0befec3c4bd83e7fda59","tid":1959874,"uid":60344,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"4月7日<br />\n沒有iPhone 9的第二日<br />\n雨<br />\n<br />\n有人話，電話嘅生命同倉鼠一樣，新陳代謝快人類30倍，人類一天，等於電話30天，人類一年，等於電話30年&hellip;&hellip;電話嘅平均壽命約2－3年，其他牌子好多機都用唔到咁耐，但我部SE都一樣，到第3年要靠換電續命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然換左電，但年老嘅身體依然承受唔住新iOS，舊電倒水咁倒，除非體積變大，否則好難應付將來嘅iOS14<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排好多post都開盤，賭會唔會又再一次被Apple 撚化<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔會！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相信APPLE！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"44e18b43e369fb4977c1efc9058a883c5c3a1fb2","tid":1959874,"uid":331235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:33:57.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"3